title: Here Come the Waves 1940 DVDR Bing Crosby musical
description:
Here Come the Waves 1940
Bing Crosby 
Betty Hutton
Sonny Tufts

directed by Mark Sandrich

Paramount musical

99 minutes

Synopsis: Sisters Rosemary and Susie Allison (Betty Hutton) are successful nightclub performers. Their act is about to come to a close when serious-minded Rosemary announces she's joining the Waves. Fun-loving Susie decides to enlist also, especially after she learns that crooner Johnny Cabot (Bing Crosby) has just been drafted by the Navy.
